course.subject: SCIE
course.name: Scientific Understanding of our Physical and Biological World
course.description: This course aims to provide students an overall scientific understanding of our world. This course will deal with fundamental questions, such as: Where does this universe come from? What is the origin of matter? What is the origin of life? What guides the human behavior? What shapes the development of the human society? What will be the future of this world? Graded DI/PA/F.
